description: Papaya BBQ is a top-notch mobile catering business bringing world class fusion barbeque experiences to the central Ohio region. Our award winning slow-smoked barbeque will melt in your mouth and leave you wanting more time after time. Our loyal customers once knew us as Buckeye Back Ribs. We're the same great barbeque company now with a little Hawaiian kick. Give our new fusion recipes a try or stick to our southern style award winning BBQ. Now more than ever, our Homestyle Has More Style®.
name: Papaya BBQ company
